flowRoot.flowPara: We also need mechanic walkways, not just machine pipes.

text.tspan: 1) Every component must have exactly 1 fix spot (never multiple)
2) Every fix spot must be reachable from every other fix spot
through a network of mechanic walkways.
3) Ideally, the travel distance between 2 fix spots is never too big.
In this example, traveling from fix spot A to fix spot C requires
going around and taking the bridge.
That's fine because the bridge is still nearby.
